diff:1609514386:1609514386:=1,77d0%0a%3c !!!1.12.2020%0a%3c '''Miele-LXIV'''%0a%3c * [[https://apps.apple.com/de/app/miele-lxiv/id988332475?mt=12 | Miele-LXIV for macOS Big Sur]] is ready.%0a%3c !!!17.11.2020%0a%3c '''AmiKo/CoMed'''%0a%3c * [[https://www.ywesee.com/AmiKo/OSX | AmiKo/CoMed]] for macOS Big Sur is out.%0a%3c !!!19.10.2020%0a%3c '''Nature.com'''%0a%3c * [[https://www.nature.com/articles/s41397-020-00195-4 | Pharmacogenetic information in Swiss drug labels  a systematic analysis]]%0a%3c !!!31.8.2020%0a%3c '''yopenedi'''%0a%3c * [[https://github.com/zdavatz/yopenedi | yopenedi]] Opentrans %3c-> EDIFACT Converter for Orders, Orders-Dispatch, Orders-Response and Invoice.%0a%3c !!!20.8.2020%0a%3c '''AmiKo Linux'''%0a%3c * [[https://github.com/zdavatz/amiko_linux | AmiKo for Linux]] is coming along just fine.%0a%3c !!!15.6.2020%0a%3c '''Corona'''%0a%3c * Attach:Multizentrische_Beobachtungsstudie_zur_Bestimmung_der_Verbreitung_des_Coronavirus_und_Entwicklung_der_Immunität_in_der_Schweiz.pdf%0a%3c !!!12.6.2020%0a%3c '''Ruby'''%0a%3c * Finding and fixing a Bug in [[https://github.com/ruby/date/issues/20 | Ruby Date 3.0.0]]%0a%3c !!!2.6.2020%0a%3c '''AmiKo/CoMed Windows'''%0a%3c * [[https://www.ywesee.com/AmiKo/Windows | AmiKo/CoMed 1.0.18.0 Release]] with Cloud- and Android Sync via Gdrive.%0a%3c * Windows 7 Installers are here: [[http://pillbox.oddb.org/Amiko_Desitin_Win7.msi | AmiKo]], [[http://pillbox.oddb.org/Comed_Desitin_Win7.msi | CoMed]]%0a%3c !!!7.5.2020%0a%3c '''OpenSource Contact Tracing Solutions'''%0a%3c * Contact tracing by [[https://spreadit.eggze.com/ | eggze]], see also [[Eggze/SpreadIt]]%0a%3c * Anonymous location sharing with [[https://covgeo.ch | Covgeo]]%0a%3c !!!4.5.2020%0a%3c '''AmiKo/CoMed Android'''%0a%3c * [[https://www.ywesee.com/AmiKo/Android | AmiKo/CoMed für Android]] mit Gdrive Support. %0a%3c * Rezepte, Patienten, Arztprofil, Favoriten in Gdrive speichern.%0a%3c !!!13.4.2020%0a%3c '''AmiKo/CoMed iOS'''%0a%3c * [[https://www.ywesee.com/AmiKo/OSX | AmiKo/CoMed Desitin]] neu mit iCloud Support. Alle Daten können in iCloud gespeichert werden.%0a%3c !!!9.4.2020%0a%3c '''Covid19'''%0a%3c * Pressemitteilung zu unserem [[https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/ddrobotecywesee-kollaborieren-im-bereich-opensource-software-davatz | Covid19 Dashboard]] in Zusammenarbeit mit [[https://ddrobotec.com/en/ | ddrobotec.com]].%0a%3c !!!27.3.2010%0a%3c '''BAG'''%0a%3c * [[https://www.republik.ch/2020/03/27/bald-ausgefaxt-bag-modernisiert-prozesse-fuer-datenerhebung | Das BAG hat bald ausgefaxt]].%0a%3c !!!23.3.2019%0a%3c '''AmiKo Desitin'''%0a%3c * AmiKo Desitin mit [[https://apps.apple.com/ch/app/amiko-desitin/id687642725 | iCloud Support]].%0a%3c * CoMed Desitin mit [[https://apps.apple.com/ch/app/comed-desitin/id712891884 | iCloud Support]]%0a%3c !!!20.3.2019%0a%3c '''Covid2019'''%0a%3c * Esri Covid2019 data Mapping for [[http://covid19.ddrobotec.com/ | Switzerland]]%0a%3c * Create an Map of Switzerland and plot the Covid2019 data on the [[https://github.com/zdavatz/covid2019_ch_map | Map]].%0a%3c !!!22.2.2019%0a%3c '''Miele-LXIV'''%0a%3c * Neue Version von [[Miele/MieleLXIV| Miele-LXIV]] ist ab sofort [[https://apps.apple.com/de/app/miele-lxiv/id988332475?mt=12 | verfügbar]].%0a%3c ** Updated all rendering code from OpenGL 2.1 (Legacy) to OpenGL 4.1 (Core)%0a%3c ** Improved handling of some type of non-compliant DICOM images%0a%3c ** Fixed GitHub issue #47 point 3%0a%3c ** Fixed 2D tiling menu%0a%3c ** Many smaller bug fixes and code improvements%0a%3c ** [[https://medevel.com/ttbyq-lshaa-ltshkhysy-lmjn-miele-lxiv/ | Arabic translation]]%0a%3c ** [[https://medevel.com/miele-lxiv-macos-icin-acik-kaynak-ve-ucretsiz-dicom-calisma-istasyonu-ve-goruntuleyicisi/ | Turkish translation]]%0a%3c !!!14.2.2020%0a%3c '''InfoCodex vs Google BERT'''%0a%3c *Comparing Google-BERT to InfoCodex Attach:Google_BERT_InfoCodex.pdf%0a%3c !!!29.1.2020%0a%3c '''AmiKo/CoMed'''%0a%3c * Diakritisch insensitive Suche für [[AmiKo/Index |AmiKo/CoMed]] wurde aufgeschaltet.%0a%3c * [[https://www.nzz.ch/schweiz/behinderte-babys-wegen-medikamenten-die-politik-schob-das-problem-auf-die-lange-bank-ld.1537060 | Sappinfo]] in der NZZ.%0a%3c !!!16.1.2020%0a%3c '''SAI'''%0a%3c * [[https://ywesee.slack.com/files/U27FC8WLA/FSCQKL8BU/fwd__sai_ausschreibung__publikation_fi_und_pi_via_refdata. | Ausschreibung SAI, gemäss (HMG, SR 812.21, Artikel 67 Absätze 3/4/5/6)]]%0a%3c * [[Ausschreibung/SAI | Fragen zur Ausschreibung]]%0a%3c !!!6.1.2020%0a%3c '''AmiKo/CoMed'''%0a%3c * [[https://www.ywesee.com/AmiKo/Android | AmiKo/CoMed]] für Android mit überarbeiteter Download-Funktion%0a%3c * [[https://github.com/zdavatz/remoterun | Remote-Run]] Release. Start a program located in /usr/local/bin using a browser, remotely.%0a%3c !!!1.1.2020%0a%3c '''Frohes neues Jahr!'''%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
